{"tid":186960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我細佬個小學老師","createTime":"2017-04-04T14:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T15:27:10.000Z","uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c218c82076196b6e74aa221a8947aba156e5f97","tid":186960,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:52:26.000Z","msg":"小弟我聽日考寫作，臨時冇塗改帶用，就問細佬借黎用一日<br />\n個唔知乜撚老師戇鳩到<br />\n塗改液唔撚比用，規定要用塗改帶<br />\n想當年我淨係問隔離個同學借<br />\n今時今日竟然有依啲老師存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從來淨係聽過冇帶書會比人話，都未聽過文具都會<br />\n仲要細佬驚死會比個老師發現，冇帶咪冇帶囉，條友鬼會上堂逐個check咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最膠係老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話咩借左咁佢用乜呀？<br />\nCLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5328d34336921ad9d069ffa20a6a6c06957d7ab","tid":186960,"uid":60936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"DSE用塗改液scan卷會睇唔清楚"},{"pid":"9cd848d3c5681407cddce122562c65b5c06b1f54","tid":186960,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:59:29.000Z","msg":"所以樓主就因為無塗改帶用而開post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"8284820c356554d178ec05c69dba8d17698ffa9f","tid":186960,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"<del>Btw 咁樣做法好難咩</del>"},{"pid":"7dd30651437e7318e9f322daeb8eae959ca3de42","tid":186960,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:00:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>DSE用塗改液scan卷會睇唔清楚</blockquote><br />\n?"},{"pid":"1d5b996d5045fa82b989f90c49fd7522100fd9b7","tid":186960,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T15:03:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以樓主就因為無塗改帶用而開post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？